  "ComponentID": "ESP32-WROOM-32",
  "ComponentType": "Wi-Fi + Bluetooth + Bluetooth LE System-on-Chip (SoC) Module",
  "Description": "The ESP32-WROOM-32E and ESP32-WROOM-32UE are powerful, general-purpose, low-power IoT modules integrating a dual-core Xtensa LX6 microcontroller, Wi-Fi, Bluetooth, and Bluetooth LE. They are designed for a wide range of applications from sensor networks to demanding tasks like audio streaming. The key difference is the antenna type: the WROOM-32E features an onboard PCB antenna, while the WROOM-32UE uses a connector for an external antenna.",
